Left Joystick (Drive):
\f2\b0  Two vertical sliders. Push the top slider for Forward. Push the bottom slider for Reverse. Letting go snaps to 0 and triggers the smart brake to halt the motor.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
