\uc0\u55357 \u57000 
\f1\b  HORN Button:
\f2\b0  Pressing this triggers the selected MP3 or WAV file over the drone's Bluetooth speaker. Swiping left/right on this button skips to the next/previous horn track. Double-tapping stops audio.\
