\f4\b  PART 2: STEER CONTROLLER (ESP8266)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f5\b0\fs24 \cf0 The ESP8266 is explicitly tasked with steering. Because steering servos draw massive current spikes and require hyper-fast update rates, offloading this from the Arduino prevents brown-outs and keeps steering latency extremely low.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

